<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="tone-n">tone <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /təʊn/    美 /toʊn/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>音调；语调：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a falling / rising tone 
降/升调</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>腔调；语气：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He talks in a very slow but humourous tone and nobody falls asleep in his class. 
他讲话慢条斯理但富有幽默感，所以他的课上没人睡觉。</p><footer>北师大⑤ – 15</footer></div></div>